headline: 3 High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Buy Right Now to Boost Your Passive Income
summary: Buy Dominion Energy for the 4.8% yield; keep it for the unfolding turnaround.  Western Midstream Partners pays a monster cash distribution.  The recent drop in Chevron's stock price is a solid buy opportunity.
